		When disciples are martyred they build Martyrdom energy; at 11 stacks, press [ElysiumQKey] to martyr John and invoke the Revelation
		Using [ElysiumQKey] before reaching 11 stacks calls down a divine lightning strike instead
		[c/AADDFF:More disciples grant increasing global damage, critical strike chance, and defense; 11 disciples restores life, 12 grants bonus move speed]
		[c/FF6666:With all 12 gathered: if your health falls below 30%, Judas will betray and instantly kill you (10s cooldown)]
		[c/FFD700:━━ Revelation Phase ━━]
		[c/FFD700:[ElysiumQKey] Drop a Celestial Meteor (180% damage)]
		[c/FFD700:[ElysiumRKey] Trigger the Last Three Seals Judgment (420% damage)]
		[c/FFD700:Right-click to summon the Four Horsemen in order: Pestilence, War, Famine, Death]
		[c/FFAA55:War boosts damage and crits; Famine grants massive armor penetration; Death amplifies all Meteor and War Horseman effects]
		'''
